{
  "stem": "24397.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They felt uncomfortable in not coming to my defense when things were said.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think they avoided me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think some of the things became apparent to me only later years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For example, when one of our neighbors, who used to come in to listen to these speeches-- and he was enlisted into some organization.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had a gas mask.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to have these round canisters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And apparently, all the people there were issued gas masks but not, not us, not the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I came to England, one of the first things I got was a gas mask.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe it was through a business associate of my father's, and they went to England.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And their name was Stary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made some contacts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow, the people that took my sister and I in were approached.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said that they would be willing to take two children as refugees.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then since we had sponsors, they attached us to this Kindertransport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And arrangements were made, and I have, I had a passport and a, a visa from England to be able to enter the country.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so in our case, we already knew where we were going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Most of the kids didn't know-- they-- on the transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They came there to some kind of a, a center-- adoption center.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then they would-- many of them were billeted out to various hostels and-- but in, in our particular case, we had a home to go to.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some time before-- a few months before-- that some negotiations were going on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Letters were being passed forward.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to go and have a pictures taken for a passport.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
